Within Sinitic, compare:
* {{och-l|灼|to burn; brilliant; to illuminate}}
* {{och-l|爍|to melt, fuse, shine}}
* {{och-l|爚|to shine, melt}}
* {{och-l|的|bright, brilliant; to mark in a target}}
* {{och-l|耀}}, {{och-l|燿|to shine, gleam}}
* {{och-l|霍|quickly, suddenly; lightning}}

